title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Resolving VFR map and ATC IFR clearance issues
description:
In this how to we are going to look at how to fix issues where you don't see the flight plan in the VFR map and don't have the ATC IFR clearance option. People affected by this will see this only when the flight is planned manually in an aircraft.
